ARGUMENT.

Is Justice, O Hay! to be a mockery‚ with thee alive? Is the poor to be oppressed, and the quiet votary of the Nine to gird on the sword he dreads? There, look at your humble servant, poor Johnston; he is cased in iron, bristling with arms. The links of his armour are as numerous as the scales on any fish or on the Libyan viper. From out his vizor his face and eyes alone are seen. ’Twas no enchantress that transformed me. That was all the misereant's doing (Brontotyphus). A small farm 1 have which yields oats alone, and feeds fleecy sheep. Here was my haven of life’s repose, and my hope was to Spin quiet lays in praise of my country and its heroes, and, chief among these, the Hay, who is the founder of thy line.
